nology team investigates root cause of legislative feed failure","timeoutMinutes":120,"responsibleRole":"Data Operations Engineer"},{"type":"human","title":"Execute Manual Override for Critical Updates","action":"Identify legislation enacted in past 48 hours affecting active client jurisdictions; manually ingest text via POST /api/knowledge-bases/:id/sources/text","stepNumber":5,"description":"For recently enacted legislation affecting active matters, manually ingest statutory text","timeoutMinutes":60,"responsibleRole":"Legal Research Specialist"},{"type":"automated","title":"Restore Feed and Verify","action":"Re-enable feed ingestion; run verification query across 50 states + federal; confirm all jurisdictions have < 24-hour staleness","stepNumber":6,"description":"Restore legislative feed connectivity; trigger full resync; verify all jurisdictions updated","expectedOutput":"All 51 jurisdictions (50 states + DC) confirmed updated; staleness warning removed from agent responses","timeoutMinutes":60}],"triggers":[],"tags":[],"status":"draft"}' | python3 -c "import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('id',''))")
